{"name": "odoo14-addon-account-move-exception", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-account-move-exception", "version": "14.0.1.0.1.dev9", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/account-invoicing", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo14-addon-base-exception", "odoo"], "summary": "Custom exceptions on account move", "upload_time": 1705719215}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Faccount--invoicing-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/account-invoicing\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/account-invoicing/tree/14.0/account_move_exception\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/account-invoicing-14-0/account-invoicing-14-0-account_move_exception\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/account-invoicing&target_branch=14.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Account Move Exception\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:c2b10fa780684a137b4b471fae53bcd0c3f850de0a36621fdc86abb121afcdf7\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis module allows you attach several customizable exceptions to your\naccount move in a way that you can filter moves by exceptions type and fix them.\n\nThis is especially useful in an scenario for mass accounts move import, because it's likely some moves have\nerrors when you import them (like product not found in Odoo, wrong line\nformat etc.)\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/website/image/ir.attachment/5784_f2813bd/datas\n:alt: Try me on Runbot\n:target: https://runbot.odoo-community.org/runbot/95/13.0\n```\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/account-invoicing/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/account-invoicing/issues/new?body=module:%20account_move_exception%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- ForgeFlow\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Miquel Ra\u00efch \\<<mailto:miquel.raich@forgeflow.com>>\n- Pimolnat Suntian \\<<mailto:pimolnats@ecosoft.co.th>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/account-invoicing](https://github.com/OCA/account-invoicing/tree/14.0/account_move_exception) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_move_exception.wizard", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_move_exception.wizard.account_exception_confirm", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.account_move_exception.wizard..account_exception_confirm", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_move_exception.models", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_move_exception.models.account_move", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.account_move_exception.models..account_move", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_move_exception.models.account_move_line", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.account_move_exception.models..account_move_line", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_move_exception.models.exception_rule", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.account_move_exception.models..exception_rule", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_move_exception.models.exception_rule", "documentation": ["Copyright 2021 ForgeFlow (http://www.forgeflow.com)", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl.html)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_move_exception.models.exception_rule.ExceptionRule", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.account_move_exception.models.exception_rule.ExceptionRule._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_move_exception.models.exception_rule.ExceptionRule.account_move_ids", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.addons.account_move_exception.models.exception_rule.ExceptionRule.model", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "instance_variables": [], "inner_classes": [], "documentation": []}],